74
00:05:50.456 --> 00:05:53.126
Goo Gil.

75
00:05:54.425 --> 00:05:57.066
Goo Gil.

76
00:05:59.196 --> 00:06:01.035
- Hey. - Goo Gil.

77
00:06:01.105 --> 00:06:02.865
- Goo Gil. - Are you awake?

78
00:06:06.475 --> 00:06:08.076
