90
00:06:35.436 --> 00:06:38.605
Do you remember anything about the assailant?

91
00:06:39.206 --> 00:06:40.506
Did you see his face?

92
00:06:41.076 --> 00:06:42.376
No.

93
00:06:43.045 --> 00:06:45.675
It all happened so fast.

94
00:06:52.415 --> 00:06:53.485
Guys.

95
00:06:53.725 --> 00:06:54.985
- Soo Jin. - Soo Jin.

96
00:06:55.485 --> 00:06:56.655
Are you all right?

97
00:06:58.626 --> 00:07:01.295
Why did you come? It's nothing serious.

98
00:07:01.425 --> 00:07:04.196
I heard you got hurt. How could I not come?

99
00:07:06.095 --> 00:07:07.965
Jae Hyun, you came too.

100
00:07:08.006 --> 00:07:10.675
Of course. I was really worried about you.

101
00:07:10.675 --> 00:07:12.235
Thank you...

102
00:07:12.836 --> 00:07:14.475
