103
00:07:14.675 --> 00:07:16.516
Thank goodness you didn't get hurt more.

104
00:07:17.845 --> 00:07:20.215
By the way, did you catch the culprit?

105
00:07:20.246 --> 00:07:22.686
No, not yet.

106
00:07:24.415 --> 00:07:25.485
Goo Gil.

107
00:07:25.956 --> 00:07:28.186
I'll catch him no matter what.

108
00:07:28.725 --> 00:07:29.826
Don't worry.

109
00:07:31.996 --> 00:07:33.996
I have to go back to the scene.

110
00:07:34.165 --> 00:07:36.165
My colleagues must be there by now.

111
00:07:36.326 --> 00:07:38.436
Please take good care of him.

112
00:07:38.436 --> 00:07:41.035
Pil, be careful.

113
00:07:44.336 --> 00:07:46.235
- Bye. - Be careful.

114
00:07:48.545 --> 00:07:50.415
I can't believe this.

115
00:07:50.415 --> 00:07:51.646
What happened?

116
00:07:51.646 --> 00:07:53.485
I'm not sure.

117
00:07:53.485 --> 00:07:54.915
Goodness.

118
00:08:01.655 --> 00:08:04.396
Gosh. Please get out of the way.

119
00:08:07.896 --> 00:08:09.066
How is the victim?

120
00:08:09.066 --> 00:08:10.235
He didn't get any serious injury.

121
00:08:10.235 --> 00:08:11.965
I left after I saw him wake up.

122
00:08:12.535 --> 00:08:14.735
Did you find any evidence?

123
00:08:14.735 --> 00:08:16.936
No. Nothing at all. It's perfectly clean.

124
00:08:16.936 --> 00:08:19.035
He's terribly cunning.

125
00:08:31.516 --> 00:08:33.985
We need to check that surveillance camera.

126
00:08:35.456 --> 00:08:37.026
(Police)

127
00:08:52.336 --> 00:08:53.375
Wait.

128
00:08:54.406 --> 00:08:56.145
This guy is suspicious.

129
00:08:56.375 --> 00:08:58.176
Yes. Other than the victims,

130
00:08:58.176 --> 00:09:01.345
he's the only person who entered the scene.

131
00:09:01.745 --> 00:09:03.416
Zoom in.

132
00:09:06.015 --> 00:09:07.426
He's slim.

133
00:09:07.826 --> 00:09:09.786
He's about 180cm tall.

134
00:09:10.656 --> 00:09:13.125
His face is completely covered.

135
00:09:13.895 --> 00:09:17.166
It'd be nice if we have something more concrete.

136
00:09:17.696 --> 00:09:19.965
Let's go back to the scene...

137
00:09:19.965 --> 00:09:21.066
tomorrow morning.

138
00:09:21.066 --> 00:09:22.206
Yes, sir.

139
00:09:23.676 --> 00:09:25.576
He covered his whole face with a mask.

140
00:09:46.196 --> 00:09:47.666
There has been...

141
00:09:47.666 --> 00:09:49.895
another assault in the heart of Seoul.

142
00:09:50.365 --> 00:09:52.465
Last night, in a tunnel in Eunha-gu,

143
00:09:52.465 --> 00:09:56.066
a man assaulted Mr. Park for no reason.

144
00:09:56.066 --> 00:09:59.605
Then he attacked Mr. Yang, a witness.

145
00:09:59.605 --> 00:10:01.706
The police started an investigation.

146
00:10:02.406 --> 00:10:04.515
The police released...

147
00:10:04.515 --> 00:10:06.745
the surveillance video of the suspect...

148
00:10:06.745 --> 00:10:09.046
and announced him as being wanted.

149
00:10:09.046 --> 00:10:10.715
What are you watching?

150
00:10:10.755 --> 00:10:14.125
Jae Hyun. Goo Gil's case is on the news.

151
00:10:14.125 --> 00:10:17.556
The attacker was caught on tape.

152
00:10:17.725 --> 00:10:20.995
He was wearing a black cap and a black mask.

153
00:10:22.395 --> 00:10:23.696
Let's eat breakfast.

154
00:10:23.696 --> 00:10:25.036
- Okay. - The continuous...

155
00:10:25.036 --> 00:10:26.095
- assaults... - Wait.

156
00:10:26.906 --> 00:10:29.536
Jae Hyun, what happened to your neck?

157
00:10:29.536 --> 00:10:30.676
Did you get hurt?

158
00:10:30.735 --> 00:10:32.706
No, it's a shaving nick.

159
00:10:32.706 --> 00:10:35.546
That must hurt. Let me get some ointment.

160
00:10:35.546 --> 00:10:37.576
It's okay. I'll do it.

161
00:10:37.645 --> 00:10:39.245
- What? - Let's eat.

162
00:10:39.316 --> 00:10:41.145
Okay. It might leave a scar.

163
00:10:42.615 --> 00:10:44.316
There.

164
00:10:46.385 --> 00:10:49.086
Pil said he was on the case.

165
00:10:49.086 --> 00:10:50.355
Did he find anything?

166
00:10:50.355 --> 00:10:52.056
Well, I'm not sure.

167
00:10:52.056 --> 00:10:53.666
I haven't talked to him.

168
00:10:53.666 --> 00:10:55.326
I'll ask him when I see him.

169
00:10:55.426 --> 00:10:56.495
Okay.

170
00:10:56.895 --> 00:10:58.995
Jae Hyun, I'll get your suit out.

171
00:10:58.995 --> 00:11:00.235
Eat up.

172
00:11:00.235 --> 00:11:01.235
Okay.

173
00:11:08.745 --> 00:11:11.316
We secured a surveillance video.

174
00:11:11.316 --> 00:11:13.686
Was it this man?

175
00:11:15.845 --> 00:11:18.186
I'm not sure. I don't remember.

176
00:11:18.615 --> 00:11:21.355
He's dazed. Please catch the culprit.

177
00:11:21.586 --> 00:11:24.095
Hello. I have a question to ask you.

178
00:11:24.196 --> 00:11:26.965
There was an assault over there last night.

179
00:11:26.965 --> 00:11:28.326
I'm looking for a man.

180
00:11:28.426 --> 00:11:30.235
Have you seen this man?

181
00:11:31.036 --> 00:11:32.395
No.

182
00:11:33.066 --> 00:11:34.166
All right.

183
00:11:37.135 --> 00:11:39.436
Have you been waiting long?

184
00:11:39.436 --> 00:11:41.245
Hi, how are you?

185
00:11:41.245 --> 00:11:42.406
Not well.

186
00:11:42.406 --> 00:11:46.546
Did the attacker look like this?

187
00:11:46.885 --> 00:11:48.015
I'm not sure.

188
00:11:48.015 --> 00:11:50.215
I was completely out of it then.

189
00:12:10.706 --> 00:12:13.375
What? Goo Gil was assaulted?

190
00:12:13.375 --> 00:12:15.505
Yes. It was on the news.

191
00:12:16.446 --> 00:12:18.676
So that news was about Goo Gil?

192
00:12:19.176 --> 00:12:20.916
Goodness.

193
00:12:21.215 --> 00:12:22.786
Is Goo Gil okay?

194
00:12:22.786 --> 00:12:24.556
He's in the hospital.

195
00:12:24.556 --> 00:12:26.316
His injury isn't serious,

196
00:12:26.316 --> 00:12:27.625
but I was so shocked.

197
00:12:27.625 --> 00:12:30.225
Gosh, I can't believe it.

198
00:12:30.755 --> 00:12:33.395
What kind of madman would do that?

199
00:12:33.965 --> 00:12:35.166
I know.

200
00:12:35.666 --> 00:12:37.635
Don't go out at night.

201
00:12:37.635 --> 00:12:39.436
You be careful.

202
00:12:39.436 --> 00:12:42.536
Tell Jae Hyun to come home early.

203
00:12:42.965 --> 00:12:45.436
Even grown men are getting beat up.

204
00:12:45.436 --> 00:12:47.306
I don't feel safe.

205
00:12:47.706 --> 00:12:49.005
Me neither.

206
00:12:49.706 --> 00:12:51.916
I told Jae Hyun to close the pharmacy early.

207
00:12:52.245 --> 00:12:56.046
By the way, how are you and Jae Hyun doing?

208
00:12:56.046 --> 00:12:58.755
We're doing well.

209
00:13:00.056 --> 00:13:02.485
Be nice to Jae Hyun.

210
00:13:02.485 --> 00:13:04.255
I haven't seen anyone...

211
00:13:04.255 --> 00:13:06.196
as nice as Jae Hyun.

212
00:13:06.696 --> 00:13:08.666
Goodness, all right.

213
00:13:13.865 --> 00:13:14.965
This...

214
00:13:15.765 --> 00:13:18.105
is the kimchi and dried filefish Jae Hyun likes.

215
00:13:18.105 --> 00:13:20.105
Take them home with you.

216
00:13:20.105 --> 00:13:22.176
Yes! Thanks, Mom.

217
00:13:22.176 --> 00:13:24.515
I'll give some to Goo Gil too.

218
00:13:24.615 --> 00:13:25.745
All right.

219
00:13:47.505 --> 00:13:50.076
I think the juice truck is closed today.

220
00:13:50.306 --> 00:13:51.536
What happened?

221
00:13:52.536 --> 00:13:53.975
Can you call her and find out what happened?

222
00:13:53.975 --> 00:13:54.975
Yes, sir.

223
00:13:58.176 --> 00:13:59.176
Hello?

224
00:13:59.446 --> 00:14:02.115
Is the juice truck not open today?

225
00:14:02.186 --> 00:14:04.916
I want to order some drinks for our meeting.

226
00:14:06.625 --> 00:14:08.026
I see.

227
00:14:08.485 --> 00:14:10.796
Okay, bye.

228
00:14:11.595 --> 00:14:12.595
What did she say?

229
00:14:12.595 --> 00:14:14.326
She says it's closed for today.

230
00:14:16.696 --> 00:14:18.135
Did something happen?

231
00:14:20.666 --> 00:14:22.836
- Open up. - Okay.

232
00:14:27.105 --> 00:14:28.276
It's good to be hurt...

233
00:14:28.946 --> 00:14:30.745
because you feed me yourself like this.

234
00:14:31.576 --> 00:14:32.745
Shall I not recover?

235
00:14:32.845 --> 00:14:35.286
Stop the nonsense and eat up.

236
00:14:35.385 --> 00:14:37.215
Give me more meat.

237
00:14:38.885 --> 00:14:40.485
Here. Open up.

238
00:14:43.026 --> 00:14:44.355
You're eating.

239
00:14:44.826 --> 00:14:46.595
- You're here, Soo Jin. - Hi.

240
00:14:46.865 --> 00:14:48.595
- Are you okay? - I'm okay.

241
00:14:49.495 --> 00:14:52.465
My mom gave me some side dishes to share with you.

242
00:14:52.995 --> 00:14:54.836
I made enough side dishes for him.

243
00:14:54.936 --> 00:14:56.735
But thanks, Soo Jin.

244
00:14:56.936 --> 00:14:58.605
You must be going through a lot.

245
00:14:59.375 --> 00:15:02.176
I saw it on the news about your case.

246
00:15:02.676 --> 00:15:03.816
I saw it too.

247
00:15:04.375 --> 00:15:05.475
By the way,

248
00:15:05.845 --> 00:15:07.985
I might be famous because of it. What do you think?

249
00:15:07.985 --> 00:15:09.885
It's not something to be happy about.

250
00:15:09.885 --> 00:15:12.215
Don't butt in others' business from now on.

251
00:15:12.215 --> 00:15:13.355
You aren't even good at fighting.

252
00:15:13.355 --> 00:15:15.385
I wasn't feeling well that day.

253
00:15:15.385 --> 00:15:16.385
Hit him some more.

254
00:15:16.385 --> 00:15:18.355
- Gosh, it hurts. - You need more beating.

255
00:15:19.696 --> 00:15:20.725
Pil, you're here.

256
00:15:22.495 --> 00:15:23.495
Hi.

257
00:15:25.965 --> 00:15:27.436
I didn't know you're here, Soo Jin.

258
00:15:27.635 --> 00:15:28.635
Hi.

259
00:15:29.105 --> 00:15:31.676
Did you find out anything about the culprit?

260
00:15:32.306 --> 00:15:33.306
Nothing yet.

261
00:15:33.475 --> 00:15:35.276
I've talked to all the victims,

262
00:15:35.276 --> 00:15:37.316
and they said they didn't see his face.

263
00:15:37.316 --> 00:15:38.316
I have no clue.

264
00:15:38.316 --> 00:15:39.316
Hey,

265
00:15:40.115 --> 00:15:42.546
I have something to say to you about it.

266
00:15:44.855 --> 00:15:46.416
When I woke up,

267
00:15:46.416 --> 00:15:48.225
I remembered something.

268
00:15:48.456 --> 00:15:49.456
What is it?

269
00:15:49.725 --> 00:15:53.156
I think there was a scar on his wrist.

270
00:15:53.895 --> 00:15:55.566
- A scar? - Yes.

271
00:15:56.026 --> 00:15:57.865
It wasn't a small scar.

272
00:15:57.865 --> 00:16:00.365
It was pretty big.

273
00:16:01.635 --> 00:16:03.906
Jung Ae, can you get me a pen and a paper?

274
00:16:03.906 --> 00:16:04.906
Okay.

275
00:16:06.235 --> 00:16:07.276
Look.

276
00:16:08.005 --> 00:16:11.316
Like this. He had a long scar...

277
00:16:11.946 --> 00:16:13.345
on his wrist like this one.

278
00:16:16.656 --> 00:16:17.656
Right.

279
00:16:18.255 --> 00:16:19.656
Something like this one.

280
00:16:35.465 --> 00:16:37.406
Right, that's him.

281
00:16:38.276 --> 00:16:39.336
What do you mean?

282
00:16:39.605 --> 00:16:41.306
Well...

283
00:16:41.745 --> 00:16:45.745
I've seen a man with a scar like this before.

284
00:16:45.916 --> 00:16:47.916
- Who is that man? - Who is that punk?

285
00:16:48.046 --> 00:16:50.715
I caught him beating up a person then too.

286
00:16:50.715 --> 00:16:52.056
But I missed him in the end.

287
00:16:52.485 --> 00:16:53.956
I think it's the same person.

288
00:16:53.956 --> 00:16:56.556
You should've caught him then.

289
00:16:56.796 --> 00:16:58.956
Who on earth is doing this?

290
00:16:58.995 --> 00:17:01.166
I'm sure he's a lunatic.

291
00:17:01.926 --> 00:17:02.926
Dal Soo.

292
00:17:03.696 --> 00:17:05.635
I'll report this to the headquarters...

293
00:17:05.635 --> 00:17:07.605
so that they refer to it in their investigation.

294
00:17:07.736 --> 00:17:10.336
All right. Let's get him for certain.

295
00:17:10.375 --> 00:17:12.076
I want to see that punk's face.

296
00:17:12.205 --> 00:17:13.875
Please catch him for us.

297
00:17:18.816 --> 00:17:19.816
Soo Jin.

298
00:17:19.945 --> 00:17:21.615
You have a lot of stuff, I'll take you to home.

299
00:17:21.615 --> 00:17:22.645
It's fine.

300
00:17:22.645 --> 00:17:24.316
It seems heavy.

301
00:17:24.415 --> 00:17:26.056
No, I'm okay. It's not heavy.

302
00:17:26.986 --> 00:17:29.185
We're friends. You can accept this kind of favor.

303
00:17:29.185 --> 00:17:32.595
I won't be able to treat you like I did before...

304
00:17:32.655 --> 00:17:34.665
since you have hateful feelings toward Jae Hyun.

305
00:17:35.595 --> 00:17:36.935
We need some time.

306
00:17:37.365 --> 00:17:38.466
Bye.

307
00:17:39.336 --> 00:17:40.336
Soo Jin.

308
00:18:10.296 --> 00:18:11.566
Jae Hyun...

309
00:18:12.036 --> 00:18:14.806
You know how I become when I get mad.

310
00:18:16.006 --> 00:18:18.105
If you try to see her once again,

311
00:18:18.675 --> 00:18:21.506
I won't let it slide, so you better behave.

312
00:18:39.326 --> 00:18:41.095
If I can't have him,

313
00:18:46.236 --> 00:18:47.966
no one can have him.

314
00:19:04.556 --> 00:19:07.125
There's a scar on Jae Hyun's wrist too.

315
00:19:08.185 --> 00:19:09.955
I don't feel good about it.

316
00:19:10.955 --> 00:19:12.326
All right.

317
00:19:19.695 --> 00:19:20.766
Hello?

318
00:19:21.935 --> 00:19:23.536
It's me, Young Ju.

319
00:19:24.105 --> 00:19:26.036
Shall we have some tea together?

320
00:19:30.246 --> 00:19:31.316
Thank you.

321
00:19:33.786 --> 00:19:35.615
The weather is so nice.

322
00:19:35.945 --> 00:19:39.286
It would've been great to go take pictures with you.

323
00:19:39.286 --> 00:19:41.655
I know. Let's make sure to do that next time.

324
00:19:44.326 --> 00:19:47.066
I love your scarf by the way.

325
00:19:47.365 --> 00:19:49.165
Where did you get it?

326
00:19:51.635 --> 00:19:53.236
It's a gift from someone.

327
00:19:53.705 --> 00:19:54.736
Who?

328
00:19:55.135 --> 00:19:56.236
Your boyfriend?

329
00:19:56.365 --> 00:19:57.375
Yes.

330
00:19:58.036 --> 00:20:00.746
He has such good taste.

331
00:20:01.175 --> 00:20:02.375
You must be happy.

332
00:20:03.345 --> 00:20:04.516
In fact, I'm not.

333
00:20:05.976 --> 00:20:08.915
I was taken away that man by some woman.

334
00:20:09.786 --> 00:20:11.586
We dated for a long time,

335
00:20:12.955 --> 00:20:15.526
but he ended up marrying another woman.

336
00:20:17.496 --> 00:20:18.895
Goodness.

337
00:20:21.425 --> 00:20:23.435
It must be hard for you.

338
00:20:24.336 --> 00:20:25.395
It is.

339
00:20:26.836 --> 00:20:30.135
I love him very much even now.

340
00:20:35.246 --> 00:20:36.476
Cheer up.

341
00:20:36.776 --> 00:20:39.546
I'm sure you'll meet someone better than him.

342
00:20:41.516 --> 00:20:43.516
I don't need someone else.

343
00:20:44.816 --> 00:20:46.986
It has to be him.

344
00:20:51.556 --> 00:20:52.855
If there's...

345
00:20:53.226 --> 00:20:57.665
a woman who loves your husband more than you do,

346
00:20:58.095 --> 00:21:01.066
can you give up on him for her sake?

347
00:21:04.675 --> 00:21:05.806
My goodness.

348
00:21:07.105 --> 00:21:08.445
That's never going to happen.

349
00:21:09.205 --> 00:21:10.445
Why not?

350
00:21:12.175 --> 00:21:14.816
Jae Hyun was originally my man,

351
00:21:15.415 --> 00:21:17.586
so you must give him back to me!

352
00:21:19.216 --> 00:21:20.756
If it wasn't for you,

353
00:21:21.726 --> 00:21:23.355
I would've been...

354
00:21:24.056 --> 00:21:25.695
next to him now.

355
00:21:26.455 --> 00:21:28.865
You took away my place. Do you get it?

356
00:21:34.466 --> 00:21:35.466
Who...

357
00:21:36.435 --> 00:21:37.635
are you?

358
00:21:38.306 --> 00:21:39.306
Me?

359
00:21:41.605 --> 00:21:43.076
I am...

360
00:21:43.645 --> 00:21:45.516
Jae Hyun's lover.

361
00:21:47.486 --> 00:21:48.915
Let me give you a warning.

362
00:21:49.546 --> 00:21:52.056
You won't be able to live with him for a long time.

363
00:21:52.455 --> 00:21:54.955
Because I'm the only one...

364
00:21:56.355 --> 00:21:57.895
who can handle him.

365
00:22:02.095 --> 00:22:03.635
You're crazy.

366
00:22:06.665 --> 00:22:08.205
You're crazy.

367
00:22:09.905 --> 00:22:11.476
I have nothing more to say,

368
00:22:13.205 --> 00:22:14.945
so I'll go.

369
00:22:16.915 --> 00:22:18.046
Did you know...

370
00:22:19.316 --> 00:22:20.385
he was convicted for assault...

371
00:22:20.385 --> 00:22:22.445
and was hospitalized in a mental institute before?

372
00:22:31.526 --> 00:22:32.855
See?

373
00:22:34.066 --> 00:22:35.996
You can't handle him.

374
00:22:36.895 --> 00:22:38.635
I don't trust what you say.

375
00:22:40.635 --> 00:22:41.966
I don't trust you at all.

376
00:23:02.090 --> 00:23:05.322
<font color="#80ffff">[VIU Ver] Episode 13 Manhole "Did You Know Him Well?"</font>
<font color="#ff80ff">-= Ruo Xi =-</font>

377
00:23:20.546 --> 00:23:22.205
Come to your senses.

378
00:23:25.276 --> 00:23:26.586
Come to your senses.

379
00:23:27.816 --> 00:23:29.216
She's just a crazy woman.

380
00:23:32.086 --> 00:23:33.185
You shouldn't...

381
00:23:35.086 --> 00:23:36.355
trust what she said.

382
00:23:51.105 --> 00:23:53.135
(The Security Footage of Random Assault Found)

383
00:24:01.445 --> 00:24:03.256
Goodness, this is rather annoying.

384
00:24:16.195 --> 00:24:17.266
Is this a travel agency?

385
00:24:18.336 --> 00:24:20.105
I want to travel to the UK.

386
00:24:21.105 --> 00:24:22.105
Yes.

387
00:24:28.945 --> 00:24:30.476
Who's this?

388
00:24:30.776 --> 00:24:33.845
Oh, her? She's the one who found your phone.

389
00:24:33.845 --> 00:24:36.385
I met her again while I was taking some pictures.

390
00:24:37.516 --> 00:24:39.556
- Really? - Isn't she pretty?

391
00:24:43.326 --> 00:24:44.455
I'm sure it's not the case.

392
00:24:46.526 --> 00:24:47.695
It can't be.

393
00:24:53.435 --> 00:24:54.466
I'm home.

394
00:24:57.405 --> 00:24:58.576
Oh, hey.

395
00:24:58.935 --> 00:25:00.205
Is something going on?

396
00:25:00.976 --> 00:25:02.246
You don't look so well.

397
00:25:02.705 --> 00:25:05.145
Is it because your friend got hurt?

398
00:25:05.875 --> 00:25:06.885
No.

399
00:25:08.645 --> 00:25:11.355
Anyway, Jae Hyun.

400
00:25:15.756 --> 00:25:17.756
Do you remember the woman...

401
00:25:18.256 --> 00:25:21.665
who found your phone for you?

402
00:25:23.435 --> 00:25:25.266
Are you acquainted with her?

403
00:25:26.165 --> 00:25:27.865
Why do you ask?

404
00:25:29.365 --> 00:25:30.405
I...

405
00:25:31.336 --> 00:25:33.175
met Ms. Park Young Ju today.

406
00:25:35.445 --> 00:25:37.175
And she said...

407
00:25:38.445 --> 00:25:42.286
she dated you for a long time.

408
00:25:44.286 --> 00:25:45.486
Is that true?

409
00:25:45.955 --> 00:25:47.026
Yes.

410
00:25:57.466 --> 00:25:59.266
Then why did you ask me...

411
00:26:00.435 --> 00:26:02.665
like you didn't know her when I showed you?

412
00:26:02.966 --> 00:26:04.536
I didn't want...

413
00:26:05.506 --> 00:26:06.905
you to know about her.

414
00:26:10.046 --> 00:26:11.216
When I saw that picture,

415
00:26:11.915 --> 00:26:14.286
I figured she was trying to get to you.

416
00:26:15.185 --> 00:26:17.185
I went over to tell her to stop seeing you.

417
00:26:17.556 --> 00:26:18.556
But...

418
00:26:19.316 --> 00:26:21.026
I guess she didn't listen.

419
00:26:21.026 --> 00:26:22.155
I mean,

420
00:26:24.595 --> 00:26:26.455
you're a married man now.

421
00:26:27.296 --> 00:26:29.066
What's with her?

422
00:26:29.066 --> 00:26:30.895
If you met her, I'm sure you know by now...

423
00:26:31.496 --> 00:26:33.306
that she is mentally unstable.

424
00:26:33.705 --> 00:26:36.405
She's been stalking me and watching me...

425
00:26:37.076 --> 00:26:38.736
even after we broke up.

426
00:26:39.435 --> 00:26:42.246
She put me through a period of rough time.

427
00:26:43.076 --> 00:26:45.845
I thought about taking legal measures,

428
00:26:46.615 --> 00:26:49.786
but she was still someone I dated.

429
00:26:49.786 --> 00:26:51.316
So I couldn't go that far.

430
00:26:53.885 --> 00:26:54.986
Jae Hyun.

431
00:26:56.695 --> 00:27:00.425
You should've told me about this before.

432
00:27:01.365 --> 00:27:03.566
Do you know how shocked I was today?

433
00:27:06.736 --> 00:27:08.935
I'm sorry, Soo Jin.

434
00:27:09.905 --> 00:27:11.036
It's all my fault.

435
00:27:14.046 --> 00:27:16.816
You said she's mentally unstable.

436
00:27:18.546 --> 00:27:20.786
I'm sure you couldn't do anything about her.

437
00:27:26.726 --> 00:27:28.385
You must have been very surprised.

438
00:27:29.726 --> 00:27:33.296
I'll do something to make sure...

439
00:27:33.665 --> 00:27:34.895
she doesn't come near you.

440
00:27:35.966 --> 00:27:37.365
Okay.

441
00:27:39.296 --> 00:27:40.905
You should be careful too.

442
00:27:42.236 --> 00:27:43.306
Okay.

443
00:27:49.915 --> 00:27:51.175
Hello.

444
00:27:51.816 --> 00:27:53.016
Hello.

445
00:27:53.185 --> 00:27:56.115
Seok Tae, do you remember that park...

446
00:27:56.115 --> 00:27:58.786
with that manhole we closed up.

447
00:27:58.786 --> 00:27:59.955
Yes, why?

448
00:27:59.955 --> 00:28:01.385
What's happening with the maintenance?

449
00:28:01.385 --> 00:28:04.326
Someone reported that the cement is shattered.

450
00:28:04.326 --> 00:28:05.496
What?

451
00:28:10.296 --> 00:28:14.165
Goodness, Pil. He must be insane.

452
00:28:14.665 --> 00:28:16.105
What did he use?

453
00:28:17.336 --> 00:28:18.905
My gosh, where did he get this?

454
00:28:21.145 --> 00:28:23.816
Where is he right now? I'll get him.

455
00:28:24.216 --> 00:28:25.516
I'll kill him.

456
00:28:26.375 --> 00:28:27.786
A scar on his wrist?

457
00:28:28.046 --> 00:28:30.615
The victim said he had a long scar on his wrist.

458
00:28:30.615 --> 00:28:31.786
It was shaped like this.

459
00:28:33.115 --> 00:28:35.355
Don't you think this can be used as a lead?

460
00:28:35.355 --> 00:28:38.425
How can we find this guy with a scar?

461
00:28:38.425 --> 00:28:40.425
We can't go around searching for scars.

462
00:28:40.425 --> 00:28:42.796
We need some suspects to check their scars.

463
00:28:42.796 --> 00:28:45.266
It's better than nothing.

464
00:28:45.266 --> 00:28:47.736
We might find someone if we single out...

465
00:28:47.736 --> 00:28:49.605
an ex-convict with a scar on their wrist.

466
00:28:49.605 --> 00:28:51.336
Hand it over to the detective in charge.

467
00:28:51.336 --> 00:28:52.605
Yes, sir.

468
00:28:52.605 --> 00:28:55.175
How's your friend doing?

469
00:28:55.645 --> 00:28:58.016
Oh, he's still in the hospital.

470
00:28:58.016 --> 00:29:00.615
But he's recovering faster than I thought.

471
00:29:01.615 --> 00:29:03.185
That's a relief.

472
00:29:03.185 --> 00:29:06.286
I'm sure you're bummed out because of your friend,

473
00:29:06.286 --> 00:29:08.425
but hand over the case to the detective in charge,

474
00:29:08.425 --> 00:29:10.155
and keep it up in this patrol division.

475
00:29:10.155 --> 00:29:11.195
Yes, sir.

476
00:29:12.355 --> 00:29:13.625
Hey, Pil.

477
00:29:14.395 --> 00:29:16.026
Did you do that to the manhole at the park?

478
00:29:16.026 --> 00:29:17.236
What's with him?

479
00:29:17.236 --> 00:29:18.665
No, don't worry.

480
00:29:18.665 --> 00:29:20.865
I'll take care of this one.

481
00:29:20.865 --> 00:29:22.336
Hey, let's talk outside.

482
00:29:22.336 --> 00:29:24.605
- Yes, but... - Move, move.

483
00:29:24.605 --> 00:29:26.105
Come out.

484
00:29:26.605 --> 00:29:28.476
We need to talk.

485
00:29:29.705 --> 00:29:31.415
Are you crazy?

486
00:29:31.415 --> 00:29:32.546
Why did you do that?

487
00:29:32.546 --> 00:29:34.786
Were you trying to time travel again?

488
00:29:34.786 --> 00:29:37.486
Think about how desperate I was.

489
00:29:37.655 --> 00:29:39.415
You wouldn't do anything for me,

490
00:29:39.415 --> 00:29:40.586
so I had to do that myself.

491
00:29:40.586 --> 00:29:43.425
Are you into some kind of a new age religion?

492
00:29:43.425 --> 00:29:45.056
Is it called the Holy Manhole?

493
00:29:45.155 --> 00:29:47.566
You've been kind of crazy recently.

494
00:29:47.566 --> 00:29:49.865
I understand that you cannot believe me.

495
00:29:50.266 --> 00:29:52.736
But think about how I felt when I asked you for that.

496
00:29:52.736 --> 00:29:54.236
I knew I would come off as crazy.

497
00:29:54.236 --> 00:29:56.266
Do you understand how desperate I am?

498
00:29:56.935 --> 00:30:00.276
Fine, let's say what you said is true.

499
00:30:00.276 --> 00:30:02.905
Why are you trying to travel through time?

500
00:30:09.615 --> 00:30:11.016
Because I'm not happy.

501
00:30:12.486 --> 00:30:14.655
This isn't the reality which I chose.

502
00:30:15.056 --> 00:30:16.355
No matter how much I try,

503
00:30:16.355 --> 00:30:18.496
I can't change anything in this reality.

504
00:30:25.165 --> 00:30:26.195
Hey.

505
00:30:26.905 --> 00:30:30.236
If you sound this serious all of a sudden,

506
00:30:31.076 --> 00:30:32.806
did you think I would believe you?

507
00:30:32.976 --> 00:30:34.306
I'm warning you.

508
00:30:34.306 --> 00:30:35.845
If you do this again,

509
00:30:35.845 --> 00:30:37.845
I'll get you fired. Okay?

510
00:30:38.615 --> 00:30:39.776
Get ahold of yourself.

511
00:30:59.266 --> 00:31:01.105
Goodness, I need to iron this shirt.

512
00:31:01.536 --> 00:31:02.736
The pants are...

513
00:31:03.105 --> 00:31:04.105
What?

514
00:31:06.506 --> 00:31:07.605
What's this?

515
00:31:19.415 --> 00:31:20.556
Jae Hyun.

516
00:31:20.955 --> 00:31:23.955
I found this inside your pocket.

517
00:31:23.955 --> 00:31:26.056
Why did you get tickets to go to the UK?

518
00:31:26.056 --> 00:31:29.226
It was a surprise, but you got me.

519
00:31:30.895 --> 00:31:33.036
It's our anniversary soon.

520
00:31:33.766 --> 00:31:35.705
You said you wanted to take pictures there,

521
00:31:35.705 --> 00:31:37.336
so I prepared those as a present.

522
00:31:39.976 --> 00:31:41.006
Jae Hyun.

523
00:31:41.006 --> 00:31:42.875
We'll close the pharmacy for a week...

524
00:31:42.875 --> 00:31:44.175
and travel there.

525
00:31:45.216 --> 00:31:46.615
Okay, then.

526
00:31:47.086 --> 00:31:48.845
Just thinking about that makes me feel excited.

527
00:31:49.746 --> 00:31:52.286
Oh, right. What happened to Goo Gil?

528
00:31:52.615 --> 00:31:54.326
He'll be discharged today.

529
00:31:55.155 --> 00:31:57.595
Did they find any lead on who did that to him?

530
00:31:57.595 --> 00:31:59.095
I don't think so.

531
00:31:59.425 --> 00:32:00.625
I mean, it was a random assault.

532
00:32:00.625 --> 00:32:02.026
He's not going to be caught easily.

533
00:32:02.026 --> 00:32:03.236
I guess you're right.

534
00:32:04.095 --> 00:32:05.296
Right.

535
00:32:05.296 --> 00:32:08.266
We have to do a homework before we go.

536
00:32:08.506 --> 00:32:10.776
- What is it? - I noticed that...

537
00:32:10.776 --> 00:32:13.776
it's Mother's birthday while we're in the UK.

538
00:32:15.175 --> 00:32:17.945
Let's meet up with her and get her a present.

539
00:32:17.945 --> 00:32:20.685
No way. You don't need to get her a present.

540
00:32:20.685 --> 00:32:23.016
I just need to give her enough cash.

541
00:32:23.016 --> 00:32:26.155
Cash? There's not much thought into that.

542
00:32:26.625 --> 00:32:27.826
Come with me.

543
00:32:28.586 --> 00:32:29.655
Okay.

544
00:32:29.655 --> 00:32:31.726
- I'll get changed. - Okay.

545
00:32:43.405 --> 00:32:44.705
Look at you.

546
00:32:45.276 --> 00:32:47.205
You should've stayed there longer.

547
00:32:47.405 --> 00:32:50.216
It's not like I'm dying.

548
00:32:50.216 --> 00:32:51.776
I needed to reopen this place too.

549
00:32:51.776 --> 00:32:54.385
You're overly diligent.

550
00:32:54.385 --> 00:32:55.885
It's not like you make a lot.

551
00:32:58.115 --> 00:32:59.286
(Assistant)

552
00:33:00.486 --> 00:33:01.526
Hello?

553
00:33:02.385 --> 00:33:05.056
Yes, I can't make a delivery today either.

554
00:33:06.895 --> 00:33:07.895
Hello?

555
00:33:08.425 --> 00:33:11.635
Yes, no. We can deliver.

556
00:33:12.766 --> 00:33:13.836
Pardon?

