00:48:40.926 --> 00:48:42.966
- Oranges! - They're fresh.

835
00:48:43.596 --> 00:48:44.636
Hello.

836
00:48:44.636 --> 00:48:47.066
You didn't go for work yet.

837
00:48:47.066 --> 00:48:48.236
I'm about to.

838
00:48:48.236 --> 00:48:49.535
- Okay. - Enjoy your time.

839
00:48:49.535 --> 00:48:50.676
Okay, bye.

840
00:48:53.276 --> 00:48:54.975
Goodness, Soo Jin.

841
00:48:55.745 --> 00:48:57.475
What happened to his face?

842
00:48:57.475 --> 00:49:00.216
Well... It's nothing.

843
00:49:00.216 --> 00:49:01.586
It's something.

844
00:49:02.346 --> 00:49:05.756
Is he the victim of the assault case?

845
00:49:05.756 --> 00:49:07.886
No, that's not it.

846
00:49:07.886 --> 00:49:10.596
Explain so I can understand!

847
00:49:10.656 --> 00:49:13.866
Who hurt my precious son-in-law?

848
00:49:13.866 --> 00:49:15.066
Who is it?

849
00:49:16.796 --> 00:49:19.066
Goodness. What brings you two here?

850
00:49:19.066 --> 00:49:20.435
That little punk.

851
00:49:20.665 --> 00:49:21.765
Look.

852
00:49:22.105 --> 00:49:23.535
Where's Pil?

853
00:49:23.676 --> 00:49:24.836
Why do you ask?

854
00:49:24.836 --> 00:49:26.375
I'm speechless.

855
00:49:26.375 --> 00:49:28.776
Can a police officer beat up a person?

856
00:49:28.776 --> 00:49:30.975
Pil beat up my son-in-law...

857
00:49:30.975 --> 00:49:33.185
that his face became a mess.

858
00:49:33.185 --> 00:49:34.486
What?

859
00:49:34.486 --> 00:49:36.685
I need to talk to Pil right now.

860
00:49:36.685 --> 00:49:38.086
Goodness.

861
00:49:38.086 --> 00:49:40.055
Pil, come out already!

862
00:49:40.055 --> 00:49:43.296
You must be mistaken. Calm down first.

863
00:49:43.296 --> 00:49:44.796
We're not mistaken.

864
00:49:44.796 --> 00:49:46.926
You all know that Pil isn't fond of...

865
00:49:46.926 --> 00:49:48.596
my son-in-law.

866
00:49:48.625 --> 00:49:51.236
What bad feelings does he have against Soo Jin...

867
00:49:51.236 --> 00:49:52.765
that he spent his entire life tormenting her?

868
00:49:52.765 --> 00:49:55.165
How long is he going to act like this?

869
00:50:09.616 --> 00:50:11.515
Pil, wake up.

870
00:50:17.895 --> 00:50:20.426
I heard you hit Jae Hyun.

871
00:50:20.426 --> 00:50:22.796
Why did you hit him? Tell us why you did that.

872
00:50:23.935 --> 00:50:25.836
Tell us already, you brat.

873
00:50:26.605 --> 00:50:27.935
I have nothing to say.

874
00:50:27.935 --> 00:50:30.575
Right, no words can justify your action.

875
00:50:30.575 --> 00:50:32.475
You took it out on him...

876
00:50:32.475 --> 00:50:35.305
because you're still not over Soo Jin, right?

877
00:50:35.305 --> 00:50:37.015
Is it really because of her?

878
00:50:37.776 --> 00:50:39.216
I'm sorry,

879
00:50:40.415 --> 00:50:42.586
but I don't want to say anything now.

880
00:50:42.616 --> 00:50:45.756
Please leave me alone.

881
00:50:45.756 --> 00:50:48.455
He's making my life so miserable.

882
00:50:48.455 --> 00:50:49.995
Why do you live like this?

883
00:50:49.995 --> 00:50:51.526
What are you going to do?

884
00:50:51.526 --> 00:50:53.966
Let's go out for now.

885
00:50:53.966 --> 00:50:55.366
Goodness.

886
00:50:55.366 --> 00:50:56.426
Let's go out.

887
00:51:05.975 --> 00:51:07.975
What? Pil hit Jae Hyun?

888
00:51:07.975 --> 00:51:11.645
Yes, so Soo Jin won't see him anymore.

889
00:51:11.645 --> 00:51:13.075
Why did he do that?

890
00:51:13.075 --> 00:51:14.616
What did he do so wrong?

891
00:51:14.616 --> 00:51:17.816
Pil drove him as the assailant.

892
00:51:18.216 --> 00:51:19.486
What?

893
00:51:19.685 --> 00:51:21.586
On what grounds?

894
00:51:21.586 --> 00:51:24.325
There's an ornament attached to his key ring.

895
00:51:24.325 --> 00:51:27.466
The broken part was found in the assault site.

896
00:51:27.466 --> 00:51:29.325
Still, he can't suspect Jae Hyun.

897
00:51:29.325 --> 00:51:30.836
He went too far.

898
00:51:30.836 --> 00:51:33.866
He didn't like Jae Hyun in the first place.

899
00:51:33.866 --> 00:51:35.665
He must've wanted to frame him.

900
00:51:35.665 --> 00:51:37.305
He's not in his right mind these days.

901
00:51:37.305 --> 00:51:40.406
He said that he time travels through a manhole.

902
00:51:40.406 --> 00:51:42.645
What nonsense is that?

903
00:51:42.645 --> 00:51:44.446
Time traveling?

904
00:51:44.446 --> 00:51:46.685
Wait a second. Hey, Pil.

905
00:51:46.685 --> 00:51:48.846
Where are you going? Come over here.

906
00:51:49.185 --> 00:51:50.915
Do you call yourself a human?

907
00:51:50.915 --> 00:51:53.055
How could you suspect Jae Hyun and hit him?

908
00:51:53.055 --> 00:51:54.926
Right, how did you manage to become...

909
00:51:54.926 --> 00:51:56.455
a police officer with those poor eyes of yours?

910
00:51:56.455 --> 00:51:58.225
He seemed to be a good guy.

911
00:51:58.256 --> 00:51:59.696
That's right.

912
00:51:59.796 --> 00:52:01.696
You went too far this time.

913
00:52:02.196 --> 00:52:04.535
Have you gone blind out of jealousy?

914
00:52:04.535 --> 00:52:07.105
You shouldn't have done that in any case.

915
00:52:07.105 --> 00:52:08.866
It's not that.

916
00:52:09.165 --> 00:52:10.736
Stop being nosy when you know nothing.

917
00:52:10.736 --> 00:52:12.105
Everyone else knows except for you...

918
00:52:12.105 --> 00:52:13.276
that he is a good guy.

919
00:52:13.276 --> 00:52:16.915
Soo Jin asked him not to report you...

920
00:52:16.915 --> 00:52:18.446
and he said okay.

921
00:52:18.446 --> 00:52:19.986
I would report you right away if I were him.

922
00:52:19.986 --> 00:52:22.486
Right. Be thankful...

923
00:52:22.486 --> 00:52:24.455
and repent, okay?

924
00:52:25.756 --> 00:52:26.955
- What? - Hey.

925
00:52:26.955 --> 00:52:27.986
Where is he going?

926
00:52:27.986 --> 00:52:30.796
He's all mad when he's the one who's at fault.

927
00:52:32.026 --> 00:52:35.566
I'm sorry for what my subordinate did to you.

928
00:52:35.566 --> 00:52:38.296
I apologize on his behalf.

929
00:52:39.336 --> 00:52:41.506
It's okay. I understand.

930
00:52:42.205 --> 00:52:44.136
He'll get punished...

931
00:52:44.136 --> 00:52:46.406
for what he's done,

932
00:52:48.305 --> 00:52:50.716
but could you forgive him and not report him?

933
00:52:50.776 --> 00:52:52.745
He's a young fellow with bright future,

934
00:52:52.745 --> 00:52:54.886
and one mistake shouldn't stop him.

935
00:52:54.986 --> 00:52:56.855
Sure, I'll let it go.

936
00:52:56.855 --> 00:52:58.285
He's not a stranger after all.

937
00:53:00.555 --> 00:53:02.256
You're so handsome...

938
00:53:02.825 --> 00:53:05.895
and broadminded as well. Thank you so much.

939
00:53:05.895 --> 00:53:07.526
I'll leave you then. Goodbye.

940
00:53:07.526 --> 00:53:08.725
Bye.

941
00:53:08.725 --> 00:53:09.966
Oh, right.

942
00:53:10.836 --> 00:53:12.696
Take these and share with your colleagues.

943
00:53:12.696 --> 00:53:15.366
Gosh, you shouldn't...

944
00:53:15.366 --> 00:53:17.236
Then I'll take just one.

945
00:53:17.236 --> 00:53:19.475
Thank you so much.

946
00:53:28.986 --> 00:53:31.386
So why did he act up?

947
00:53:43.966 --> 00:53:45.736
I just met with Mr. Park Jae Hyun.

948
00:53:47.466 --> 00:53:49.506
Thankfully, he wanted to show you mercy.

949
00:53:49.506 --> 00:53:51.435
It won't come down to the worst situation.

950
00:53:53.975 --> 00:53:56.346
You should be thankful that he's a good man.

951
00:53:57.046 --> 00:53:58.075
But still,

952
00:53:58.375 --> 00:54:01.685
you can't be forgiven for beating a civilian.

953
00:54:01.886 --> 00:54:03.986
You will be suspended for a month.

954
00:54:04.455 --> 00:54:05.455
Keep that in mind.

955
00:54:34.446 --> 00:54:35.515
No.

956
00:54:37.555 --> 00:54:38.855
People can be like that...

957
00:54:39.586 --> 00:54:40.926
when they get angry.

958
00:54:42.685 --> 00:54:43.756
It's nothing.

959
00:54:53.805 --> 00:54:55.336
Hey, wait.

960
00:54:58.935 --> 00:55:01.406
You can go ahead. I'll be right behind you.

961
00:55:01.406 --> 00:55:02.406
Sure.

962
00:55:08.216 --> 00:55:09.216
Soo Jin.

963
00:55:13.656 --> 00:55:15.225
- We need to talk. - Let go.

964
00:55:15.486 --> 00:55:16.995
I told you not to say hello to me.

965
00:55:17.495 --> 00:55:19.596
I heard you told Jae Hyun not to report me.

966
00:55:20.366 --> 00:55:21.625
Don't be delusional.

967
00:55:21.625 --> 00:55:23.125
I didn't do this for you.

968
00:55:23.265 --> 00:55:24.336
Why did you do that?

969
00:55:24.765 --> 00:55:26.366
You should've let him report me.

970
00:55:27.466 --> 00:55:30.276
I'm sure you resent and hate me for doing that.

971
00:55:30.276 --> 00:55:33.406
I thought of your parents who were so glad that...

972
00:55:33.406 --> 00:55:34.875
you finally got a job. That's why.

973
00:55:35.105 --> 00:55:36.546
If it wasn't for them,

974
00:55:36.546 --> 00:55:38.075
I would've reported you myself.

975
00:55:39.616 --> 00:55:41.015
As I told you yesterday,

976
00:55:41.015 --> 00:55:43.145
I don't think of you as a friend anymore.

977
00:55:43.386 --> 00:55:45.816
This is the last favor I do for you.

978
00:56:18.316 --> 00:56:20.625
No one will believe me.

979
00:56:22.526 --> 00:56:24.995
Soo Jin is beginning to hate me more and more.

980
00:56:31.165 --> 00:56:33.636
Each day just gets worse and worse.

981
00:56:44.245 --> 00:56:45.245
Hey.

982
00:56:46.276 --> 00:56:49.745
How can you take me away from this awful place?

983
00:56:52.685 --> 00:56:53.926
What can I do?

984
00:57:02.296 --> 00:57:04.895
What are you doing here?

985
00:57:11.975 --> 00:57:14.075
Hey, are you just getting off work?

986
00:57:14.946 --> 00:57:17.216
Are you trying to break into the manhole again?

987
00:57:18.145 --> 00:57:19.245
Don't worry.

988
00:57:19.816 --> 00:57:21.716
I don't have the energy to do that.

989
00:57:22.515 --> 00:57:23.555
Goodness.

990
00:57:24.616 --> 00:57:25.616
Hey.

991
00:57:25.785 --> 00:57:29.026
Stop causing trouble in Soo Jin's family...

992
00:57:29.026 --> 00:57:30.825
who's happily married.

993
00:57:31.125 --> 00:57:33.765
You need to get ahold of yourself.

994
00:57:33.796 --> 00:57:34.825
Sure.

995
00:57:35.596 --> 00:57:37.366
Everyone thinks I'm the bad guy.

996
00:57:38.895 --> 00:57:39.935
Would I...

997
00:57:41.265 --> 00:57:43.435
Would I do that to an innocent man?

998
00:57:43.435 --> 00:57:44.836
I don't care. Whatever.

999
00:57:44.836 --> 00:57:47.245
Anyway, anyone can see that you were wrong.

1000
00:57:47.245 --> 00:57:50.875
So you need to apologize to Jae Hyun...

1001
00:57:51.046 --> 00:57:52.575
and to Soo Jin.

1002
00:57:56.316 --> 00:57:58.855
I understand you still have feelings for her,

1003
00:57:59.515 --> 00:58:02.756
but if you like her, you can't do this to her.

1004
00:58:07.566 --> 00:58:09.466
You need to stop this for the sake...

1005
00:58:10.796 --> 00:58:12.096
of Soo Jin's happiness.

1006
00:58:41.165 --> 00:58:42.165
Welcome.

1007
00:58:44.366 --> 00:58:46.736
Wow, you don't look very well.

1008
00:58:46.966 --> 00:58:47.966
I guess so.

1009
00:58:48.906 --> 00:58:50.475
How are you feeling?

1010
00:58:51.136 --> 00:58:53.075
It seems like your wounds are healing.

1011
00:58:53.305 --> 00:58:57.015
I can really take a beating, you know.

1012
00:58:58.316 --> 00:59:00.216
I need an ointment to get rid of scars.

1013
00:59:00.216 --> 00:59:01.216
Sure.

1014
00:59:04.386 --> 00:59:07.125
You must be angry because of Pil.

1015
00:59:07.586 --> 00:59:11.125
He's been a bit odd since when he was a kid.

1016
00:59:12.596 --> 00:59:14.895
I thank you so much...

1017
00:59:15.125 --> 00:59:16.665
for showing him mercy.

1018
00:59:16.665 --> 00:59:17.696
It's nothing.

1019
00:59:17.696 --> 00:59:19.265
He's Soo Jin's friend too.

1020
00:59:19.906 --> 00:59:20.906
Here you are.

1021
00:59:30.745 --> 00:59:31.745
What is it?

1022
00:59:32.075 --> 00:59:33.346
Oh, it's nothing.

1023
00:59:35.515 --> 00:59:37.616
- How much is this? - Five dollars.

1024
00:59:37.616 --> 00:59:40.355
Five dollars. Here you are.

1025
00:59:42.256 --> 00:59:43.395
See you later.

1026
00:59:43.656 --> 00:59:44.756
Goodbye.

1027
00:59:51.866 --> 00:59:54.805
That looks like the scar which I saw on that day.

1028
01:00:00.645 --> 01:00:02.705
No, I doubt it.

1029
01:00:05.216 --> 01:00:06.276
It can't be him.

1030
01:00:07.716 --> 01:00:08.785
It can't be.

1031
01:00:09.185 --> 01:00:10.486
Gosh, my back.

1032
01:00:11.355 --> 01:00:13.055
Should I pack more long sleeves?

1033
01:00:16.895 --> 01:00:17.955
You're home.

1034
01:00:18.026 --> 01:00:19.300
You're right on time.

1035
01:00:19.325 --> 01:00:20.696
Where's your suitcase?

1036
01:00:20.696 --> 01:00:23.196
I'm packing up, but I don't see your suitcase.

1037
01:00:23.196 --> 01:00:25.596
It's in my trunk.

1038
01:00:25.665 --> 01:00:26.736
I'll bring it.

1039
01:00:26.906 --> 01:00:28.636
No. I'll go.

1040
01:00:28.636 --> 01:00:30.836
You should go and wash up. Key, please.

1041
01:00:31.906 --> 01:00:33.245
- Thank you. - Sure.

1042
01:01:01.535 --> 01:01:02.535
Here it is.

1043
01:01:07.006 --> 01:01:08.875
What's this?

1044
01:01:15.816 --> 01:01:16.816
What?

1045
01:01:30.895 --> 01:01:33.705
He was wearing a black cap and a black mask.

1046
01:01:33.705 --> 01:01:36.265
Jae Hyun was originally my man,

1047
01:01:36.906 --> 01:01:38.975
so you must give him back to me!

1048
01:01:39.006 --> 01:01:40.105
Do you know...

1049
01:01:40.805 --> 01:01:41.875
he was convicted for assault...

1050
01:01:41.875 --> 01:01:43.915
and was hospitalized in a mental institute before?

1051
01:02:00.296 --> 01:02:01.665
No.

1052
01:02:04.165 --> 01:02:05.636
It can't be.

1053
01:02:08.466 --> 01:02:10.776
It's can't be you, Jae Hyun.

1054
01:02:49.276 --> 01:02:52.375
(Manhole)

1055
01:02:53.116 --> 01:02:54.316
Come quickly.

1056
01:02:54.785 --> 01:02:56.145
I need to tell you something.

1057
01:02:56.586 --> 01:02:59.386
Soo Jin got into a hit-and-run accident.

1058
01:02:59.386 --> 01:03:01.355
You need to save Soo Jin!

1059
01:03:01.355 --> 01:03:03.495
I can't live if something happens to Soo Jin.

1060
01:03:03.656 --> 01:03:05.756
Can you please let me open up this manhole?

1061
01:03:06.296 --> 01:03:08.665
I was the one who said...

1062
01:03:08.895 --> 01:03:10.395
nothing bad will ever happen to you.

1063
01:03:10.566 --> 01:03:13.435
Do you remember anything about the accident?

1064
01:03:14.366 --> 01:03:17.935
I'll bring the evidence, so just you wait.

